channel.title: I need a list or some Korean Social Security Numbers
channel.description: I would like a list or some Korean Social Security Numbers. I would like to play the OPEN BETA of Ragnarok Online 2, and for the registration it required a Korean Social Security Number. So if anyone can get me 1 or a list of them, I will be grateful. I have googled for an hour and didn't find any correct results. kthxbai :)
